Nigerians have reacted after three All Progressives Congress (APC) Governors on Friday met Rivers Governor, Nyesom Wike, at his private residence in Port Harcourt.The Governors, who arrived in the afternoon to meet with Wike, were Kayode Fayemi (Ekiti); Babajide Sanwo-Olu (Lagos) and Rotimi Akeredolu (Ondo). APC leaders met with Wike at the private residence of the Rivers State governor in Port Harcourt on Friday afternoon. As of the filing of this report, the closed-door meeting is ongoing with its details yet unknown, but it may not be unconnected with the 2023 presidential election. Some Nigerians took to social media to react to the development. Below are some of the reactions. goldmynemusic wrote; ”Coup in the making” ike_igbo_xyz wrote; ‘‘Wike just wan give Atiku heart attack” phyzee07 wrote; ‘‘They don’t really care about us…..Nigeria politics it’s all about personal interest” -Advertisement- POLL otunbaayodeji1 wrote; ”Omoh these people are just playing up with them citizens” iamoracle1 wrote; The hint is already showing in Wike’s cap style wamsea wrote; ”Is that not Fayose with them? Hmmm” _bishopgram wrote; ”Now I know why Tinubu no want Ambode for second term. Ambode can’t be this loyal, Ambode can be everywhere for baba.”